Class Comet

java.lang.Object
  Space_Object
      Comet
Direct Known Subclasses:
Comet6, Comet7
abstract class Comet
extends Space_Object

Class Comet - Space objects that bounce againsts walls. Have collisions with all other objects. Destroyed if it hits a star or planet. Sucked in by black holes. Can be two types, comet6 and comet7 which are subclasses of this superclass.

Version:
2016.03.13
